{"tid":2311508,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教聯會左校洗腦式宣揚國家憲法日 校長執小紅書嗌「母親」學生在家須肅立唱國歌","createTime":"2020-12-04T06:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T07:53:22.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"57de948c39eb4309562a4c4930a00e2001141a27","tid":2311508,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"政府多次強調要加強憲法及《基本法》教育， 教育局局長楊潤雄昨（3日）再撰文指，憲法日是學校推動學生國民身份認同的好機會。香港教育工作者聯會黃楚標學校今早在校內舉行升旗儀式，更挪用全日四節課堂中的兩節，舉行憲法教育活動。該校校長兼教聯會會長黃錦良稱，從過去一年香港發生的事可見年輕人應對憲法有更多認識，今年亦會特別向同學強調守法意識及國民身份認同，惟表示不會安排學生觀看政府舉辦的網上座談會。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201204/SEJVH2HAHJD2XDA3RRL3UIZGCE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201204%2FSEJVH2HAHJD2XDA3RRL3UIZGCE%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGKxOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=d9908094\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201204%2FSEJVH2HAHJD2XDA3RRL3UIZGCE%2F&h=14082cb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201204/SEJVH2HAHJD2XDA3RRL3UIZGCE/</a>"},{"pid":"e0c3ff11817ef499d8085f732a447a30fd4f24bf","tid":2311508,"uid":186997,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3u6YcPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3u6YcPU.jpg&h=887169c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1fc0485f61f3759de765cf8316172ed4fa6f459","tid":2311508,"uid":75765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"被人屌老母，可以用國安法告佢"},{"pid":"da34830c9bd5bf5b30987e381562178cd6b11f87","tid":2311508,"uid":185656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:22:54.000Z","msg":"你哋係乜嘢呀？<br />\n支那人～啪啪啪！支那人～啪啪啪！"},{"pid":"83dbbc90773be02438454e10775eeb3f1e1e08a1","tid":2311508,"uid":370061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T06:24:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span 